<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>跑跑卡丁车 on Orztu The Way | Orz途</title><link>https://www.orztu.com/tags/%E8%B7%91%E8%B7%91%E5%8D%A1%E4%B8%81%E8%BD%A6/</link><description>Recent content in 跑跑卡丁车 on Orztu The Way | Orz途</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><copyright>Orztu The Way</copyright><lastBuildDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2019 17:52:17 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.orztu.com/tags/%E8%B7%91%E8%B7%91%E5%8D%A1%E4%B8%81%E8%BD%A6/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>跑跑卡丁车手游 L1 驾照“下坡漂移”教程</title><link>https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/</link><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jul 2019 17:52:17 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="popkart-l1-4-cut.mp4" &gt;&amp;raquo;&amp;gt;视频地址&amp;laquo;&amp;lt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;首先我们要在前两个门集满第一管氮气。&lt;br&gt;
1号门前向右轻打方向调整车头，然后向左拖漂。&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-01.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-01_hu_bcbd989194404acb.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-01_hu_f00c86f088a564a2.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;右漂经过2号门然后向左拉正车头后使用第一个氮气。&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-02.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-02_hu_eff4044932c2a79c.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-02_hu_c7a5a511ca409942.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;立即向右拖漂经过3号门。&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-03.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-03_hu_dfb64cdd34a355.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-03_hu_25543b8d83b7a8e1.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;氮气满之后马上拉正车头。&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-04.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-04_hu_f07f3266cc8fef4c.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-04_hu_e06d0ef0406d46ad.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;继续使用氮气，然后拖漂经过4号门，同样气满之后回正。&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-05.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-05_hu_bf5edb9004d9946f.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-05_hu_70b5dcf6f2354c78.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;趁氮气未结束，再次拖漂经过5号门，然后马上使用氮气。&lt;br&gt;
5号门相对前面两个门不用漂那么大。&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-06.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-06_hu_d7c29ad8ddd3504c.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-06_hu_86740cdfbc859f2f.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;过了5号门氮气满了断位拉头，然后接左漂继续集气并过6号门。&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-07.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-07_hu_dbac709a8dc06199.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-07_hu_a8bce00ea5028b7e.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-08.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-08_hu_e2e4e5804537acb1.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-08_hu_1822f35471a43309.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;7号门前这个小坎需要小漂一下，不然落地容易弹起。&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-09.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-09_hu_58cba136131752e9.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-09_hu_f05ee7026031f315.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;落地走一点点之后，向左轻漂，不要太大。&lt;br&gt;
因为已经有两个氮气了，漂满了这一管就浪费了。&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-10.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-10_hu_a5f4b4fc788ce6c5.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-10_hu_228ab5e284108dd7.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;过这个坎向右轻漂，然后落地马上使用氮气。&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-11.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-11_hu_56ce469e22b1f729.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-11_hu_b03d9c528dbf64cc.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-12.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-12_hu_7bfd505685eed84c.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-12_hu_9f3bc7178c1a3141.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;然后把刚才没满的氮气漂满，这样又有两个氮气了。&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-13.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-13_hu_71b6bf5c4f579cef.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-13_hu_6875783dc5578489.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;紧接着再次把氮气漂到快满，以便下坡起跳之后集气。&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-14.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-14_hu_3c4bb48c55e88a1.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-14_hu_769abf6c453868fb.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;使用氮气加速下坡，起跳前向左轻漂，不要用力。&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-15.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-15_hu_dc7179cf2ac394dc.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-15_hu_c5130c28e20352f7.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;落地之后氮气满了马上使用氮气纠正车头，避免撞墙；&lt;br&gt;
如果前面失误，这个时候没有氮气，可以再次向左漂避免撞墙。&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-16.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-16_hu_e56598cabeebca9a.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-16_hu_e868c024a347e5b5.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这个坎前向右漂移过弯，同样满了就用氮气回正；&lt;br&gt;
如果没有氮气可用，就向左拉车头集气，然后使用氮气。&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-17.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-17_hu_8589eeba38ac39c8.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-17_hu_e9a2306eaf8b9f32.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;下一个弯车速起来就向左拖漂过弯，并集满一管气。&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-18.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-18_hu_1e3077391af64b94.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-18_hu_b0a2e3600cb094d3.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;出弯后使用氮气，调整位置，准备从外道插入下一个弯。&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-19.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-19_hu_38f64ed3d8b9207e.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-19_hu_26700b47c4c9464c.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;这个弯向右打死，出弯使用氮气或者断位拉头。-&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-20.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-20_hu_27d155cedc624697.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-20_hu_4b766be790fa70ca.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;出弯之后等速度起来拖漂过最后一个弯。&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-21.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-21_hu_b86b738c477596c0.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-21_hu_56604faa4c828a8f.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;最后一下起跳前向左轻漂。&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-22.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-22_hu_e6fd628e134a0541.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-22_hu_c923a238c9f1390a.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;剩余的直线就交给氮气了。&lt;br&gt;
&lt;img src="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-23.png"
width="858"
height="396"
srcset="https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-23_hu_5eca3fd32c17db0a.png 480w, https://www.orztu.com/post/popkart-l1-4/popkart-l1-4-23_hu_a6baff15aa32b699.png 1024w"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="216"
data-flex-basis="520px"
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;a class="link" href="popkart-l1-4-cut.mp4" &gt;&amp;raquo;&amp;gt;视频地址&amp;laquo;&amp;lt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$ N_{2}O $ 本是笑气，但在跑跑里面被大家称为“氮气”&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>